cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.AR 

This paper deals with the problem of reducing the computational complexity of deep neural networks, which is a common concern in computer vision (cs.CV), machine learning (cs.LG), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) research. The proposed method involves quantization of weight parameters and activations, which is also relevant to the field of neural networks (cs.NE). Additionally, the paper discusses the hardware implications of the proposed method, which could be relevant to the field of computer architecture (cs.AR).
